[{"Code":"en","Title":"Features","Slug":"payment-sessions-features","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"588c336a-fb9e-4191-8cfc-f9d78083629b\">Payment Session includes features designed to simplify your tokenization process and improve the success rate. It helps ensure the purpose of tokenization is correctly identified and managed.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"753\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:753px;width:753px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:377px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c2616423-7c99-4a4f-bf02-50cedc1c6fd1\">Features</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2ff57945-5f8e-4135-a11c-faa374227e74\">Descriptions</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"27af6eae-4794-40c4-9654-46c55c16043e\">Save</p><p data-block-id=\"aedaab96-6973-4e4a-a33e-2b5143855b9d\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"10a41317-e3a6-4654-bb16-1e7da53dc80b\">Generate a payment token to save an end user’s payment information for future transactions using type <code>SAVE</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c8d09d51-0737-4a1e-8f52-f93e5c99d375\">PCI compliant card data collection using Xendit-hosted checkout UI</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"d964b668-1746-4813-a909-9569ce492a0c\">Tokenize your customer card details without the need to be PCI certified. Our Xendit-hosted checkout UI helps to handle sensitive card information collection</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"bb7a403d-38ae-46ab-8f3c-bdc3feec5438\">Card on file tagging</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9391eae6-b9f0-4c04-bdca-24319dc0bbc2\">Increase payment success rates by tagging transactions accurately for proper processing</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"9012198c-263b-40a0-ae83-dce13b3a0b07\">Card recurring configuration tagging</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9e6a2989-b65f-457a-bea0-ca79564860a6\">Increase payment success rates by defining recurring payment schedule accurately for proper processing</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"32c5c73a-a258-4caa-86d3-c7b2d0946c7f\">Cards BIN whitelist</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"89deebd5-9006-49e3-99fd-a191bbdca07b\">The Xendit-hosted page can be configured to accept payments only from specific BINs (Bank Identification Numbers) as defined during Payment Session creation</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-7cx2dk-004\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-i23bky-005\"><strong>Limitation</strong></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1153\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1153px;width:1153px;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" dir=\"ltr\" border=\"1\" data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-baot=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:184px;\"><col style=\"width:337px;\"><col style=\"width:330px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzjeh-pgjjhn-010\"><strong>Feature Parity</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-l99g63-049\"><strong>Descriptions</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-kkf6ie-050\"><strong>Workaround</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-h90g1u-051\"><strong>ETA</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-vl1duj-052\">One time payment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-heno6g-053\">Accept one time payment for a customer present flow</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwq2a6-c2so5c-184\">AVAILABLE NOW</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd36-lszydk-198\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-cm0u1e-056\">Manual authorization </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-6564mp-057\">Create authorization for future manual capture. This is available for Cards only</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-9oh0ex-058\">AVAILABLE NOW</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-ybz1dm-059\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-yi6osj-060\">Pay and Save</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-i681zw-061\">Not only session parity, but Xendit never support pay and save at the same time using our hosted page.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ol data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-2wx981-064\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">Use payment session with type SAVE first</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">Once merchant get the payment token, they can directly trigger Pay with   token flow in Payment API v3</p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"> <em>to note this workaround might impact double authentication (OTP/3DS) experience to end user if merchant doesn’t have MIT creds/eligibility</em></p></li></ol></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-bl3yxb-063\">Q4 2025</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq05a-hsl55r-067\">Component</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq5av-xyrmen-068\">We don’t have proper and full compliance solution for merchant to have their own checkout UI but want to embbed our component in their hosted page (especially for cards, this is important to follow PCIDSS compliance). </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrvxoq-ld3hcv-070\">For now, we only have cards_session_js flow for merchants, but do not overselling this. As default, always sell our hosted page solution (payment session with mode payment link) to merchants. </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrz6tz-73awqh-071\">Ongoing project, ETA 2026</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\">Invoice &lt;&gt; Session Feature parity</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwesj3-gggsr4-158\">Invoice Feature</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwez5x-7sd7dz-159\">Availability on Session</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwf1hy-l8dd2o-160\">Notes</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfjfg-8ffwzk-161\">Notifications</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfmg9-1ynavs-162\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-tna252-164\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">We need to assess first on how much notification impact the success rate</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">Right now, payment session can only be integrated through API - means merchant MUST have a “store” and customer is present - notification wont add much value yet</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhbcp-7gw3e7-166\">Installment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwheva-yc65ln-167\">Q1 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd39-lgkwrr-199\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhj6j-otc53z-168\">Callback virtual account or fixed va</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhuna-8wh8mp-169\">Won’t be here</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwi50i-deizqz-170\">it’s a legacy feature of invoice which against the purpose of Xendit hosted page function itself. </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkoxo-1j8r5g-171\">Creation from dashboard</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkvdp-wscyz7-172\">Q2 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwl0ar-opt4gk-173\">It will be new tab on dashboard - minimize breaking flow of existing invoice</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwpfcq-ezftu7-183\">Multiple payment link </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwsxdc-kgkslo-185\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwt2jl-aji0al-186\">Collecting demands first as this is low usage</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtbbl-4cfw0v-187\">Batch payment link</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtglf-fd3z0s-188\">SUNSET</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd3b-tb134s-200\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlglv-hll649-174\">UI customization (previously called invoice setting)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlx18-cnec65-175\">Q3 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwm04w-szinmn-176\">Our hosted page now is clean and generic</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwmjvv-6w8qup-177\">Fees</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwn99k-kmusr9-178\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-scglc6-180\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">Still assessing how much value of this feature - since it does nothing but “displaying” and not necessary surcharge end user the transaction fee</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">Merchant can use items or description</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz44m-8jafp0-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz1us-fmxuko-007\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-1eew8m-006\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Features","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Fitur","Slug":"payment-sessions-features","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mc27isp7-hcumd9-023\">Payment Session mencakup fitur yang dirancang untuk menyederhanakan proses tokenisasi Anda dan meningkatkan tingkat keberhasilan. Ini membantu memastikan tujuan tokenisasi diidentifikasi dan dikelola dengan benar.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"753\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:753px;width:753px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:377px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1ji-alw335-025\">Fitur</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1ji-55c2k0-026\">Deskripsi</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1ji-kz5wfu-027\">Simpan</p><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1ji-rhecpz-028\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jj-nwdcmr-029\">Membuat token pembayaran untuk menyimpan informasi pembayaran pengguna akhir untuk transaksi mendatang menggunakan jenis <code>SAVE</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jj-agctk9-030\">Pengumpulan data kartu yang sesuai dengan PCI menggunakan UI checkout yang dihosting Xendit</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jj-4cihdl-031\">Tokenisasi detail kartu pelanggan Anda tanpa perlu bersertifikat PCI. UI checkout kami yang dihosting Xendit membantu menangani pengumpulan informasi kartu sensitif</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jj-dql2l9-032\">Pemberian tag kartu pada file</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-9ag2pu-033\">Tingkatkan tingkat keberhasilan pembayaran dengan menandai transaksi secara akurat untuk pemrosesan yang tepat</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-5oojsr-034\">Pemberian tag konfigurasi berulang kartu</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-f224cd-035\">Tingkatkan tingkat keberhasilan pembayaran dengan menentukan jadwal pembayaran berulang secara akurat untuk pemrosesan yang tepat</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-fl725g-036\">Daftar putih BIN Kartu</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-x57xjt-037\">Halaman yang dihosting Xendit dapat dikonfigurasi untuk menerima pembayaran hanya dari BIN (Nomor Identifikasi Bank) tertentu seperti yang ditentukan selama pembuatan Payment Session</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mc27j1jk-7zrc69-038\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Fitur","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"คุณสมบัติ","Slug":"features-2","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"588c336a-fb9e-4191-8cfc-f9d78083629b\">Payment Session มีฟีเจอร์ที่ออกแบบมาเพื่อทำให้กระบวนการ tokenization ของคุณง่ายขึ้นและปรับปรุงอัตราความสำเร็จให้ดีขึ้น ซึ่งช่วยให้มั่นใจได้ว่าวัตถุประสงค์ของการ tokenization ได้รับการระบุและจัดการอย่างถูกต้อง</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"753\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:753px;width:753px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:377px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c2616423-7c99-4a4f-bf02-50cedc1c6fd1\">ฟีเจอร์</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2ff57945-5f8e-4135-a11c-faa374227e74\">คำอธิบาย</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"27af6eae-4794-40c4-9654-46c55c16043e\">Save</p><p data-block-id=\"aedaab96-6973-4e4a-a33e-2b5143855b9d\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"10a41317-e3a6-4654-bb16-1e7da53dc80b\">สร้าง payment token เพื่อบันทึกข้อมูลการชำระเงินของผู้ใช้ปลายทางสำหรับการทำธุรกรรมในอนาคตโดยใช้ type <code>SAVE</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c8d09d51-0737-4a1e-8f52-f93e5c99d375\">การรวบรวมข้อมูลบัตรที่สอดคล้องกับ PCI โดยใช้ Xendit-hosted checkout UI</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"d964b668-1746-4813-a909-9569ce492a0c\">Tokenize รายละเอียดบัตรของลูกค้าของคุณโดยไม่จำเป็นต้องได้รับการรับรอง PCI (PCI certified) Xendit-hosted checkout UI ของเราช่วยจัดการการรวบรวมข้อมูลบัตรที่ละเอียดอ่อน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"bb7a403d-38ae-46ab-8f3c-bdc3feec5438\">Card on file tagging</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9391eae6-b9f0-4c04-bdca-24319dc0bbc2\">เพิ่มอัตราความสำเร็จในการชำระเงินโดยการติดแท็กธุรกรรมอย่างแม่นยำสำหรับการประมวลผลที่เหมาะสม</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"9012198c-263b-40a0-ae83-dce13b3a0b07\">Card recurring configuration tagging</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9e6a2989-b65f-457a-bea0-ca79564860a6\">เพิ่มอัตราความสำเร็จในการชำระเงินโดยการกำหนดตารางการชำระเงินแบบ recurring อย่างแม่นยำสำหรับการประมวลผลที่เหมาะสม</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"32c5c73a-a258-4caa-86d3-c7b2d0946c7f\">Cards BIN whitelist</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"89deebd5-9006-49e3-99fd-a191bbdca07b\">Xendit-hosted page สามารถกำหนดค่าให้ยอมรับการชำระเงินจาก BINs (Bank Identification Numbers) ที่ระบุไว้เท่านั้น ตามที่กำหนดไว้ในระหว่างการสร้าง Payment Session</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-7cx2dk-004\"><strong>บันทึกส่วนตัว</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-i23bky-005\"><strong>ข้อจำกัด</strong></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1153\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1153px;width:1153px;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" dir=\"ltr\" border=\"1\" data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-baot=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:184px;\"><col style=\"width:337px;\"><col style=\"width:330px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzjeh-pgjjhn-010\"><strong>ความเท่าเทียมกันของฟีเจอร์ (Feature Parity)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-l99g63-049\"><strong>คำอธิบาย</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-kkf6ie-050\"><strong>วิธีแก้ไขปัญหาเฉพาะหน้า (Workaround)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-h90g1u-051\"><strong>ETA</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-vl1duj-052\">การชำระเงินครั้งเดียว (One time payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-heno6g-053\">ยอมรับการชำระเงินครั้งเดียวสำหรับ customer present flow</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwq2a6-c2so5c-184\">พร้อมใช้งานแล้ว</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd36-lszydk-198\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-cm0u1e-056\">การอนุมัติด้วยตนเอง (Manual authorization)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-6564mp-057\">สร้าง authorization สำหรับการ capture ด้วยตนเองในอนาคต ซึ่งใช้ได้เฉพาะกับ Cards เท่านั้น</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-9oh0ex-058\">พร้อมใช้งานแล้ว</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-ybz1dm-059\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-yi6osj-060\">Pay and Save</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-i681zw-061\">ไม่เพียงแต่ความเท่าเทียมกันของ session เท่านั้น แต่ Xendit ไม่เคยรองรับ Pay and Save พร้อมกันโดยใช้ hosted page ของเรา</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ol data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-2wx981-064\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">ใช้ payment session ที่มี type SAVE ก่อน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">เมื่อ merchant ได้รับ payment token แล้ว พวกเขาสามารถเรียกใช้ Pay with token flow ใน Payment API v3 ได้โดยตรง</p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"> <em>โปรดทราบว่าวิธีแก้ไขปัญหานี้อาจส่งผลกระทบต่อประสบการณ์การยืนยันตัวตนสองชั้น (OTP/3DS) สำหรับผู้ใช้ปลายทาง หาก merchant ไม่มีข้อมูลรับรอง/คุณสมบัติ MIT</em></p></li></ol></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-bl3yxb-063\">Q4 2025</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq05a-hsl55r-067\">Component</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq5av-xyrmen-068\">เรายังไม่มีโซลูชันที่เหมาะสมและสอดคล้องตามข้อกำหนดอย่างสมบูรณ์สำหรับ merchant ที่ต้องการมี checkout UI ของตนเอง แต่ต้องการฝัง component ของเราใน hosted page ของพวกเขา (โดยเฉพาะอย่างยิ่งสำหรับ cards ซึ่งเป็นสิ่งสำคัญในการปฏิบัติตามข้อกำหนด PCIDSS)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrvxoq-ld3hcv-070\">สำหรับตอนนี้ เรามีเพียง cards_session_js flow สำหรับ merchants เท่านั้น แต่ไม่ควรขายเกินความจำเป็น โดยค่าเริ่มต้น ให้ขายโซลูชัน hosted page ของเราเสมอ (payment session ที่มี mode payment link) ให้กับ merchants</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrz6tz-73awqh-071\">โครงการที่กำลังดำเนินอยู่, ETA 2026</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\">ความเท่าเทียมกันของฟีเจอร์ Invoice &lt;&gt; Session</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwesj3-gggsr4-158\">ฟีเจอร์ Invoice</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwez5x-7sd7dz-159\">ความพร้อมใช้งานบน Session</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwf1hy-l8dd2o-160\">หมายเหตุ</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfjfg-8ffwzk-161\">การแจ้งเตือน (Notifications)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfmg9-1ynavs-162\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-tna252-164\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">เราจำเป็นต้องประเมินก่อนว่าการแจ้งเตือนส่งผลกระทบต่ออัตราความสำเร็จมากน้อยเพียงใด</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">ขณะนี้ payment session สามารถรวมเข้ากับ API เท่านั้น ซึ่งหมายความว่า merchant ต้องมี “store” และลูกค้าต้องอยู่ ณ ที่นั้น (customer is present) - การแจ้งเตือนจึงยังไม่เพิ่มมูลค่ามากนัก</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhbcp-7gw3e7-166\">การผ่อนชำระ (Installment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwheva-yc65ln-167\">Q1 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd39-lgkwrr-199\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhj6j-otc53z-168\">Callback virtual account หรือ fixed va</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhuna-8wh8mp-169\">จะไม่มีในส่วนนี้</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwi50i-deizqz-170\">เป็นฟีเจอร์เดิมของ Invoice ซึ่งขัดต่อวัตถุประสงค์ของฟังก์ชัน Xendit hosted page เอง</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkoxo-1j8r5g-171\">การสร้างจาก dashboard</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkvdp-wscyz7-172\">Q2 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwl0ar-opt4gk-173\">จะเป็นแท็บใหม่บน dashboard - เพื่อลดผลกระทบต่อ flow ของ Invoice ที่มีอยู่</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwpfcq-ezftu7-183\">Multiple payment link</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwsxdc-kgkslo-185\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwt2jl-aji0al-186\">กำลังรวบรวมความต้องการก่อน เนื่องจากมีการใช้งานต่ำ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtbbl-4cfw0v-187\">Batch payment link</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtglf-fd3z0s-188\">SUNSET</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd3b-tb134s-200\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlglv-hll649-174\">การปรับแต่ง UI (เดิมเรียกว่า invoice setting)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlx18-cnec65-175\">Q3 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwm04w-szinmn-176\">hosted page ของเราตอนนี้สะอาดและเป็นแบบทั่วไป</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwmjvv-6w8qup-177\">ค่าธรรมเนียม (Fees)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwn99k-kmusr9-178\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-scglc6-180\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">ยังคงประเมินมูลค่าของฟีเจอร์นี้อยู่ - เนื่องจากไม่ได้ทำอะไรนอกจาก “แสดงผล” และไม่จำเป็นต้องเรียกเก็บค่าธรรมเนียมการทำธุรกรรมจากผู้ใช้ปลายทาง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">Merchant สามารถใช้ items หรือ description ได้</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz44m-8jafp0-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz1us-fmxuko-007\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-1eew8m-006\"></p>","SeoTitle":"คุณสมบัติ","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Características","Slug":"payment-sessions-features","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"588c336a-fb9e-4191-8cfc-f9d78083629b\">Payment Session incluye características diseñadas para simplificar su proceso de tokenización y mejorar la tasa de éxito. Ayuda a asegurar que el propósito de la tokenización se identifique y gestione correctamente.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"753\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:753px;width:753px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:377px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c2616423-7c99-4a4f-bf02-50cedc1c6fd1\">Características</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2ff57945-5f8e-4135-a11c-faa374227e74\">Descripciones</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"27af6eae-4794-40c4-9654-46c55c16043e\">Save (Guardar)</p><p data-block-id=\"aedaab96-6973-4e4a-a33e-2b5143855b9d\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"10a41317-e3a6-4654-bb16-1e7da53dc80b\">Genere un token de pago para guardar la información de pago de un usuario final para transacciones futuras utilizando el tipo <code>SAVE</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"c8d09d51-0737-4a1e-8f52-f93e5c99d375\">Recolección de datos de tarjeta compatible con PCI utilizando la UI de checkout alojada por Xendit</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"d964b668-1746-4813-a909-9569ce492a0c\">Tokenice los detalles de la tarjeta de su cliente sin la necesidad de obtener la certificación PCI. Nuestra UI de checkout alojada por Xendit ayuda a manejar la recolección de información sensible de la tarjeta</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"bb7a403d-38ae-46ab-8f3c-bdc3feec5438\">Etiquetado de tarjeta en archivo (Card on file tagging)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9391eae6-b9f0-4c04-bdca-24319dc0bbc2\">Aumente las tasas de éxito de pago etiquetando las transacciones con precisión para un procesamiento adecuado</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"9012198c-263b-40a0-ae83-dce13b3a0b07\">Etiquetado de configuración de recurrencia de tarjeta (Card recurring configuration tagging)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"9e6a2989-b65f-457a-bea0-ca79564860a6\">Aumente las tasas de éxito de pago definiendo el calendario de pago recurrente con precisión para un procesamiento adecuado</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"377\"><p data-block-id=\"32c5c73a-a258-4caa-86d3-c7b2d0946c7f\">Lista blanca de BIN de tarjetas (Cards BIN whitelist)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"89deebd5-9006-49e3-99fd-a191bbdca07b\">La página alojada por Xendit se puede configurar para aceptar pagos solo de BINs (Números de Identificación Bancaria) específicos, según se definan durante la creación de Payment Session</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-7cx2dk-004\"><strong>Notas privadas</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-i23bky-005\"><strong>Limitación</strong></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1153\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1153px;width:1153px;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" dir=\"ltr\" border=\"1\" data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-baot=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:184px;\"><col style=\"width:337px;\"><col style=\"width:330px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzjeh-pgjjhn-010\"><strong>Paridad de Características</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-l99g63-049\"><strong>Descripciones</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-kkf6ie-050\"><strong>Solución alternativa (Workaround)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;font-weight:bold;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-h90g1u-051\"><strong>ETA</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-vl1duj-052\">Pago único (One time payment)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-heno6g-053\">Aceptar pago único para un flujo con cliente presente</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwq2a6-c2so5c-184\">DISPONIBLE AHORA</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd36-lszydk-198\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91k-cm0u1e-056\">Autorización manual (Manual authorization)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-6564mp-057\">Crear autorización para futura captura manual. Esto está disponible solo para Cards</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-9oh0ex-058\">DISPONIBLE AHORA</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-ybz1dm-059\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-yi6osj-060\">Pagar y Guardar (Pay and Save)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-i681zw-061\">No solo paridad de sesión, sino que Xendit nunca ha soportado pagar y guardar al mismo tiempo utilizando nuestra página alojada.</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><ol data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-2wx981-064\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">Utilice Payment Session con tipo SAVE primero</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mdvrgnl9-l7cudx-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-sv4jnx-062\">Una vez que el comercio obtenga el token de pago, puede activar directamente el flujo de Pago con token en Payments API v3</p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvrqjsp-kfwqtk-069\"> <em>Nota: esta solución alternativa podría impactar la experiencia de doble authentication (OTP/3DS) para el usuario final si el comercio no tiene credenciales/elegibilidad MIT</em></p></li></ol></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrg91l-bl3yxb-063\">Q4 2025</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"184\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq05a-hsl55r-067\">Componente (Component)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"337\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrq5av-xyrmen-068\">No tenemos una solución de cumplimiento adecuada y completa para que el comercio tenga su propia UI de checkout, pero quiera incrustar nuestro componente en su página alojada (especialmente para tarjetas, esto es importante para seguir el cumplimiento PCIDSS). </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"330\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrvxoq-ld3hcv-070\">Por ahora, solo tenemos el flujo cards_session_js para comercios, pero no sobrevenda esto. Por defecto, siempre venda nuestra solución de página alojada (Payment Session con modo Payment Link) a los comercios. </p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;wrap-strategy:4;word-wrap:break-word;background-color:;border-color:;text-align:;\"><p data-block-id=\"mdvrz6tz-73awqh-071\">Proyecto en curso, ETA 2026</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnzgsx-42ab0b-009\">Paridad de Características de Invoice &lt;&gt; Session</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"><col style=\"width:302px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwesj3-gggsr4-158\">Característica de Invoice</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwez5x-7sd7dz-159\">Disponibilidad en Session</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwf1hy-l8dd2o-160\">Notas</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfjfg-8ffwzk-161\">Notifications (Notificaciones)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfmg9-1ynavs-162\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-tna252-164\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">Necesitamos evaluar primero cuánto impacta la notificación en la tasa de éxito</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwg4ch-2rroh8-165\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwfsjk-ea8bsm-163\">Actualmente, Payment Session solo se puede integrar a través de API, lo que significa que el comercio DEBE tener una \"tienda\" y el cliente debe estar presente; la notificación no agregará mucho valor todavía</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhbcp-7gw3e7-166\">Installment (Pago a plazos)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwheva-yc65ln-167\">Q1 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd39-lgkwrr-199\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhj6j-otc53z-168\">Callback de Virtual Account o VA fija</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwhuna-8wh8mp-169\">No estará disponible</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwi50i-deizqz-170\">Es una característica heredada de Invoice que va en contra del propósito de la función de página alojada de Xendit. </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkoxo-1j8r5g-171\">Creación desde el dashboard</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwkvdp-wscyz7-172\">Q2 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwl0ar-opt4gk-173\">Será una nueva pestaña en el dashboard, para minimizar la interrupción del flujo de Invoice existente</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwpfcq-ezftu7-183\">Múltiples Payment Link</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwsxdc-kgkslo-185\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwt2jl-aji0al-186\">Recopilando demandas primero, ya que este es de bajo uso</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtbbl-4cfw0v-187\">Batch Payment Link</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwtglf-fd3z0s-188\">DESCONTINUADO (SUNSET)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwwd3b-tb134s-200\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlglv-hll649-174\">Personalización de la UI (anteriormente llamada configuración de Invoice)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwlx18-cnec65-175\">Q3 2026</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwm04w-szinmn-176\">Nuestra página alojada ahora es limpia y genérica</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwmjvv-6w8qup-177\">Fees (Tarifas/Comisiones)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwn99k-kmusr9-178\">TBD</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"302\"><ul data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-scglc6-180\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">Todavía estamos evaluando el valor de esta característica, ya que no hace nada más que \"mostrar\" y no necesariamente cobra una tarifa de transacción adicional al usuario final</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfwnbwj-a2bt4n-181\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfwnbpo-9muu1z-179\">El comercio puede usar artículos o descripción</p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz44m-8jafp0-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnz1us-fmxuko-007\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mdvnymdb-1eew8m-006\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Características","Description":null}]